<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{ locale }}">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% if locale == 'en' %}Your password was changed{% else %}Ihr Passwort wurde ge√§ndert{% endif %}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .security-details {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-details strong {
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .danger-box {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>
            {% if locale == 'en' %}
                Password Changed
            {% else %}
                Passwort ge√§ndert
            {% endif %}
        </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        {% if locale == 'en' %}
            {# English Version #}
            <p>Hello {{ user.nameFirst ?? 'User' }},</p>

            <p>This email confirms that your password was successfully changed.</p>

            <div class="security-details">
                <strong>Security Details:</strong><br>
                <strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{ timestamp|date('Y-m-d H:i:s T') }}<br>
                <strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ ip_address }}<br>
                <strong>Device:</strong> {{ user_agent }}<br>
                <strong>Changed by:</strong> {{ changed_by_self ? 'You' : 'Administrator' }}
                {% if not changed_by_self and changed_by_user %}
                    ({{ changed_by_user.email }})
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Information</strong><br>
                All your active sessions on all devices have been logged out for your security.
                You will need to log in again with your new password.
            </div>

            <div class="danger-box">
                <strong>üîí Wasn't you?</strong><br>
                If you did not make this change, your account may be compromised.
                <strong>Please contact support immediately.</strong>
                <br><br>
                <a href="mailto:support@example.com" class="btn">Report Unauthorized Change</a>
            </div>

            <p>If you made this change, you can safely ignore this email. Your account is secure.</p>

        {% else %}
            {# German Version #}
            <p>Hallo {{ user.nameFirst ?? 'Benutzer' }},</p>

            <p>Diese E-Mail best√§tigt, dass Ihr Passwort erfolgreich ge√§ndert wurde.</p>

            <div class="security-details">
                <strong>Sicherheitsdetails:</strong><br>
                <strong>Datum & Uhrzeit:</strong> {{ timestamp|date('d.m.Y H:i:s T') }}<br>
                <strong>IP-Adresse:</strong> {{ ip_address }}<br>
                <strong>Ger√§t:</strong> {{ user_agent }}<br>
                <strong>Ge√§ndert von:</strong> {{ changed_by_self ? 'Ihnen' : 'Administrator' }}
                {% if not changed_by_self and changed_by_user %}
                    ({{ changed_by_user.email }})
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Wichtige Sicherheitsinformation</strong><br>
                Zu Ihrer Sicherheit wurden alle Ihre aktiven Sitzungen auf allen Ger√§ten abgemeldet.
                Sie m√ºssen sich mit Ihrem neuen Passwort erneut anmelden.
            </div>

            <div class="danger-box">
                <strong>üîí Waren Sie das nicht?</strong><br>
                Falls Sie diese √Ñnderung nicht vorgenommen haben, k√∂nnte Ihr Konto kompromittiert sein.
                <strong>Bitte kontaktieren Sie umgehend den Support.</strong>
                <br><br>
                <a href="mailto:support@example.com" class="btn">Unautorisierte √Ñnderung melden</a>
            </div>

            <p>Falls Sie diese √Ñnderung vorgenommen haben, k√∂nnen Sie diese E-Mail ignorieren. Ihr Konto ist sicher.</p>

        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>
            {% if locale == 'en' %}
                This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this email.
            {% else %}
                Dies ist eine automatische Sicherheitsbenachrichtigung. Bitte antworten Sie nicht auf diese E-Mail.
            {% endif %}
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
